{"lastModified":1751885852398,"uri":"c::8346777690::vessel::05f57420-f341-11ee-ad60-95c22dfdf626","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nEmbark on an unforgettable maritime adventure aboard the Lagoon 51 named “Spring,” a masterfully crafted catamaran that redefines luxury on the open waters. This stunning vessel boasts an impressive layout, featuring four double cabins and two semi-double cabins, accommodating a total of twelve guests in lavish comfort. The interior design exudes modern elegance, providing each cabin with a private sanctuary. With four toilets onboard, convenience is a top priority, ensuring a seamless and enjoyable sailing experience for all.\n\nIn addition to its exceptional guest accommodations, “Spring” is well-equipped to cater to the needs of its crew with two dedicated single bow cabins. This thoughtful design ensures that every aspect of your journey is attended to with precision and professionalism.\n\nThe yacht’s array of amenities elevates the onboard experience to new heights. Stay cool and comfortable with air conditioning, enjoy continuous power with a generator and inverter, and revel in the convenience of a water maker. The teak cockpit and wooden foldable cockpit table create a sophisticated outdoor living space, perfect for al fresco dining or simply basking in the sea breeze.\n\nConnectivity is never an issue, thanks to the onboard WiFi, while the inclusion of a stand-up paddleboard adds an extra layer of enjoyment to your maritime escape. “Spring” is not just a vessel; it’s a floating sanctuary of luxury, where every detail has been meticulously designed to ensure an indulgent and unforgettable sailing experience. Set sail and immerse yourself in the opulence that “Spring” has to offer, as it glides through the waves, creating memories that will last a lifetime.","blueprint":{"name":"SPRING","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::05f57420-f341-11ee-ad60-95c22dfdf626::assets::11068240-412